  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "chapterTitle": "第一部分 谈话录",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300025472_4_4246-4299",
          "range": "4246-4299",
          "rangeStart": 4246,
          "rangeEnd": 4299,
          "markText": "毛主席曾经讲过，团结多数，孤立少数，利用矛盾，各个击破，在不同战略阶段，这个策略始终是我们在斗争中坚持的。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1722476645,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-08-01 09:44:05",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4246&rangeEnd=4299",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4246&rangeEnd=4299"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_12_1183-1235",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1183-1235",
      "markText": "毛主席指出不应夸大原子弹的作用，要强调人民斗争的作用。这是从政治上分析，免得长他人的志气，灭自己的威风。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1183&rangeEnd=1235",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1183&rangeEnd=1235"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_4_4254-4299",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4254-4299",
      "markText": "团结多数，孤立少数，利用矛盾，各个击破，在不同战略阶段，这个策略始终是我们在斗争中坚持的。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4254&rangeEnd=4299",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4254&rangeEnd=4299"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_11_7241-7311",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "7241-7311",
      "markText": "傅聪讲过这样的话：文艺工作者都去参加劳动，我的手如果劳动两个月，就不能弹钢琴了。少奇同志说这话有道理。确实不能要求所有的人都去参加体力劳动。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7241&rangeEnd=7311",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7241&rangeEnd=7311"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_13_779-819",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "779-819",
      "markText": "整风的方针是从团结的愿望出发，经过批评或者斗争，达到新的团结；惩前毖后，治病救人",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=779&rangeEnd=819",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=779&rangeEnd=819"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_5_3536-3581",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3536-3581",
      "markText": "本来庐山会议后就有人提出继续出《毛选》。毛主席说现在不是出《毛选》的问题，而是出《刘选》。",
      "totalCount": 104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3536&rangeEnd=3581",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3536&rangeEnd=3581"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_30_10637-10721",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "10637-10721",
      "markText": "中国一切政党的政策及其实践在中国人民中所表现的作用的好坏、大小，归根到底，看它对于中国人民的生产力的发展是否有帮助及其帮助之大小，看它是束缚生产力的，还是解放生产力的。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=10637&rangeEnd=10721",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=10637&rangeEnd=10721"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_9_1192-1238",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1192-1238",
      "markText": "当时毛主席很着急，要研究希特勒打到什么地方了。毛主席没有想到，在战争初期苏联军队那么不经打。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1192&rangeEnd=1238",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1192&rangeEnd=1238"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_14_2030-2065",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "2030-2065",
      "markText": "毛主席对美国人表现出很大的吸引力。美国人承认，毛主席使谈判者无拘无束。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=2030&rangeEnd=2065",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=2030&rangeEnd=2065"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_58_6254-6298",
      "chapterUid": 58,
      "range": "6254-6298",
      "markText": "毛主席这位伟大的革命家，比较缺少充分宽容的美德。这是他跟许多同志发生一些不愉快关系的因素",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=58&rangeStart=6254&rangeEnd=6298",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=58&rangeStart=6254&rangeEnd=6298"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_20_5504-5579",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "5504-5579",
      "markText": "“在军队党与地方党的关系中，应更多更严的要求军队党负责任。如遇争论纠纷，应更多地责备军队党。”“军队干部与地方干部关系，一般应多要求多责备军队干部。”",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=5504&rangeEnd=5579",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=5504&rangeEnd=5579"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_18_9696-9754",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "9696-9754",
      "markText": "唯在蒋没有宣布全面破裂以前，我们暂时不提反蒋，但要公开批蒋；蒋尚未提及八路军与中共，我们亦不提及整个国民党与中央军。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=9696&rangeEnd=9754",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=9696&rangeEnd=9754"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_12_4604-4664",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "4604-4664",
      "markText": "毛主席对我说：一个人要会讲话，有的同志不会讲话，打电话给我就讲半小时，一小时。陈云讲话非常简单明了，根本不占我多少时间。",
      "totalCount": 78,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=4604&rangeEnd=4664",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=4604&rangeEnd=4664"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_21_15937-15998",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "15937-15998",
      "markText": "这次，我党能够不费一枪一弹就使国民党进攻没能发动起来的重要原因，在于这时我们不但有国内统一战线，而且还建立了国际统一战线。",
      "totalCount": 78,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=15937&rangeEnd=15998",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=15937&rangeEnd=15998"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_6_2625-2700",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2625-2700",
      "markText": "毛主席发表组织起来的讲演。这是毛主席一生非常重要的思想。他一生的斗争从某一方面来说就是把人民组织起来，影响一直到解放以后，提出发展互助合作运动的问题。",
      "totalCount": 77,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2625&rangeEnd=2700",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2625&rangeEnd=2700"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_4_4035-4064",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4035-4064",
      "markText": "要从这种形势分析中，说明毛主席的思想方法就是从客观实际出发",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4035&rangeEnd=4064",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4035&rangeEnd=4064"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_8_2217-2279",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2217-2279",
      "markText": "李维汉去边区，是很重要的一着棋，这在陕甘宁边区确实起了很大的作用，特别是在协调林老、谢老和高岗之间的关系上，起了很大的作用。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025472&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2217&rangeEnd=2279",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6332bb0813ab7073g012868?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2217&rangeEnd=2279"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025472_11_7393-7457",
